'''颅顶眼'''（英文：Parietal eye），也被称为'''第三眼'''（third eye）、'''松果眼'''（pineal eye），是一些[[鱼类|鱼类]]、[[两栖类|两栖类]]、[[爬行类动物|爬行类]]动物[[上丘脑|上丘脑]]的一部分。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Parietal Eye - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/agricultural-and-biological-sciences/parietal-eye|accessdate=2021-04-03|work=|publisher=Science Direct|language=en}}</ref> 颅顶眼位于头顶，可感光，并与[[松果體|松果体]]有联系，一同负责调节[[昼夜节律|昼夜节律]]以及[[體溫調節|体温调节]]。<ref name=":0" />

== 相关物种 ==
[[File:Anolis_carolinensis_parietal_eye.JPG|右]]
拥有颅顶眼的物种包括[[喙頭蜥|喙头蜥]]、大多数[[蜥蜴|蜥蜴]]、[[蛙|蛙]]（[[无尾目|无尾目]]）、[[蠑螈科|蝾螈]]（[[有尾目|有尾目]]）、[[鲨鱼|鲨鱼]]、[[七鳃鳗科|七鳃鳗]]（Lamprey）、一些种类的硬骨鱼等。<ref>{{Cite book|title=Visual Centers in the Brain|volume=7 / 3 / 3 B|last=Dodt|first=Eberhard|date=1973|publisher=Springer, Berlin, Heidelberg|isbn=9783642654978|series=Handbook of Sensory Physiology|pages=113–140|language=en|doi=10.1007/978-3-642-65495-4_4|chapter=The Parietal Eye (Pineal and Parietal Organs) of Lower Vertebrates}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Sphenodontidae|url=http://www.embl-heidelberg.de/~uetz/families/Sphenodontidae.html|date=2003-10-07|last=Uetz|first=Peter|work=The EMBL reptile database|publisher=European Molecular Biology Laboratory, heidelberg|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070221195027/http://www.embl-heidelberg.de/~uetz/families/Sphenodontidae.html <!-- Bot retrieved archive -->|archive-date=2007-02-21|access-date=2007-02-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=The occurrence of parietal eyes in recent Lacertilia (Reptilia)|first1=GC|last2=Wurst|first2=GZ|date=1976|journal=Journal of Herpetology|issue=2|doi=10.2307/1562791|volume=10|pages=113–121|jstor=1562791|last1=Gundy}}</ref> [[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]则不具有颅顶眼，但其已灭绝的近亲[[獸孔目|兽孔目]]动物有颅顶眼。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The sixth sense in mammalian forerunners: Variability of the parietal foramen and the evolution of the pineal eye in South African Permo-Triassic eutheriodont therapsids - Acta Palaeontologica Polonica|url=http://www.app.pan.pl/article/item/app002192015.html|accessdate=2021-04-03|work=www.app.pan.pl|language=en}}</ref> 此外，[[龟鳖目|龟鳖目]]和[[主龍類|主龙类]]动物（如[[鸟类|鸟类]]和[[鳄鱼|鳄鱼]]）也不具有颅顶眼。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Archelosaurian Color Vision, Parietal Eye Loss, and the Crocodylian Nocturnal Bottleneck|url=https://doi.org/10.1093/molbev/msw265|last=Emerling|first=Christopher A.|date=2017-03-01|journal=Molecular Biology and Evolution|issue=3|doi=10.1093/molbev/msw265|volume=34|pages=666–676|issn=0737-4038}}</ref>

== 解剖学 ==
[[File:Madagascar_spiny_tailed_iguana_cropped.jpg|右]]
在相关物种中，颅顶眼比[[眼睛|双眼]]要小得多，且在现今物种中，颅顶眼被皮肤覆盖，从外界不容易观察到。<ref name="VB2">{{cite book|title=The Vertebrate Body|author=Romer, Alfred Sherwood|author2=Parsons, Thomas S.|publisher=Holt-Saunders International|year=1977|isbn=978-0-03-910284-5|location=Philadelphia, PA|pages=471–473}}</ref> 与[[脊椎动物|脊椎动物]]正常视力利用[[视杆细胞|视杆细胞]]和[[视锥细胞|视锥细胞]]进行感光不同，颅顶眼使用了不同的生化方法进行感光。<ref>{{cite journal|title=An unusual cGMP pathway underlying depolarizing light response of the vertebrate parietal-eye photoreceptor|url=http://www.nature.com/neuro/journal/v1/n5/full/nn0998_359.html|last=Xiong|first=Wei-Hong|journal=Nature Neuroscience|issue=5|doi=10.1038/1570|year=1998|volume=1|pages=359–65|pmid=10196524|author3=Yau, King-Wai|author2=Solessio, Eduardo C.|access-date=2007-02-22}}</ref>

在相关物种中，颅顶眼（松果眼）属于[[上丘脑|上丘脑]]的一部分，上丘脑还包括[[松果體|松果体]]。

